## CALCULATION

> Top 10 industry contribute the most to carbon emissions?

```sql
    SELECT ig.industry_group,
	   SUM(pe.carbon_footprint_pcf)
    FROM industry_groups ig 
	JOIN product_emissions pe ON pe.industry_group_id = ig.id 
    GROUP BY ig.industry_group 
    ORDER BY SUM(pe.carbon_footprint_pcf) DESC
    LIMIT 10;
```

| industry\_group | SUM(pe.carbon\_footprint\_pcf) |
| -------------- | ---------------------------- |
| Electrical Equipment and Machinery | 9801558 |
| Automobiles & Components | 2582264 |
| Materials | 577595 |
| Technology Hardware & Equipment | 363776 |
| Capital Goods | 258712 |
| "Food, Beverage & Tobacco" | 111131 |
| "Pharmaceuticals, Biotechnology & Life Sciences" | 72486 |
| Chemicals | 62369 |
| Software & Services | 46544 |
| Media | 23017 |

##### *Although it is in the top 10 industries with the highest carbon contribution, the Electrical Equipment and Machinery industry is the industry with the highest proportion. This is data from 2013 to 2017. With the 'carbon burden' of the Electrical Equipment and Machinery industry, there needs to be specific measures such as: 'Global emissions monitoring system'*

> Top 10 countries with the highest carbon contributions

```sql
    SELECT c.country_name AS 'country',
	   SUM(pe.carbon_footprint_pcf) AS 'pcf'
    FROM countries c 
		JOIN product_emissions pe ON pe.country_id = c.id
    GROUP BY c.country_name
    ORDER BY SUM(pe.carbon_footprint_pcf) DESC
    LIMIT 10;
```

> Which country do the top 10 products with the highest carbon contribution come from?

```sql
    SELECT c.country_name AS 'countries', 
		pe.product_name AS product_name, 
		SUM(pe.carbon_footprint_pcf) AS 'carbon_contribute'
    FROM  countries c
	JOIN product_emissions pe ON pe.country_id = c.id 
	GROUP BY c.country_name, pe.product_name
	ORDER BY SUM(pe.carbon_footprint_pcf) DESC 
    LIMIT 10;
```

> Top 5 products with the highest carbon contribution in Spain?

```sql
    SELECT pe.product_name AS product_name, 
           SUM(pe.carbon_footprint_pcf) AS 'carbon_contribute',
	   pe.industry_group_id 
    FROM  countries c
	JOIN product_emissions pe ON pe.country_id = c.id 
	WHERE c.id = 23
	GROUP BY c.country_name, pe.product_name
	ORDER BY SUM(pe.carbon_footprint_pcf) DESC 
	LIMIT 5;
```

| product\_name | carbon\_contribute | industry\_group\_id |
| ------------ | ----------------- | ----------------- |
| Wind Turbine G128 5 Megawats | 3718044 | 13 |
| Wind Turbine G132 5 Megawats | 3276187 | 13 |
| Wind Turbine G114 2 Megawats | 1532608 | 13 |
| Wind Turbine G90 2 Megawats | 1251625 | 13 |
| Lineal Alkyl Bencene (LAB) | 6999 | 14 |

##### *These wind turbine models are commonly used in the renewable energy sector, particularly for wind power generation, and contribute to Spain's efforts in transitioning towards cleaner and more sustainable sources of energy.*

##### *The utilization of turbines in Spain reflects the country's efforts to reduce carbon emissions, promote renewable energy technologies, and enhance energy efficiency.*

> What has been the trend in the carbon footprint (PCF) of the country of Spain over the years?

```sql
    SELECT
        CASE
            WHEN id LIKE '%2013' THEN '2013'
            WHEN id LIKE '%2014' THEN '2014'
            WHEN id LIKE '%2015' THEN '2015'
            WHEN id LIKE '%2016' THEN '2016'
            WHEN id LIKE '%2017' THEN '2017'
            ELSE 'other'
        END AS year_group,
    SUM(carbon_footprint_pcf) AS 'pcf'
    FROM
        product_emissions pe 
    WHERE country_id = '23' AND industry_group_id = '13'
    GROUP BY
        year_group;
```

| year\_group | pcf |
| ---------- | --- |
| 2015 | 9778464 |

##### *Addressing Emissions: To combat high carbon emissions, Spain is implementing strategies like promoting electric vehicles, increasing renewable energy capacity, enhancing energy efficiency, and setting ambitious emission reduction targets in line with international agreements like the Paris Agreement.*
